      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... they have their own lives to live, you know? their own struggles. and here i am, just a constant drain on their time and money and energy. i've always been a provider, a strong one, and now i'm just... this thing they have to manage. it feels like the kindest thing i could do for them is to just not be in the way anymore. wouldn't it be easier for them if i just stopped being a problem?",
